Severity: ${alert.severity}
Time: ${alert.timestamp}

ðŸ“Š Metrics:
â€¢ n8n: ${alert.metrics.n8n_connections}
â€¢ Total: ${alert.metrics.total_connections}/${alert.metrics.max_connections}
â€¢ Utilization: ${alert.metrics.utilization_pct}%
â€¢ Leaked: ${alert.metrics.leaked_connections}

ðŸ’¡ Actions:
${alert.recommended_actions.map((a, i) => `${i + 1}. ${a}`).join('\n')}
